page.title: 06PETT LEVEL RESCUE BOAT III
page.content: February: Search for poison canisters April: Windsurfer rescued May: Search for missing dinghy and occupants June: Rescued yacht and three people June: Took casualty from angling boat July: Towed broken-down speed-boat to Rye Harbour, 4 people landed July: Investigated unidentified object in water July: Combined search for boat on fire August:Assisted 2 speed boats August:Investigated unidentified objects in sea requested by Rye police August: Search for casualties after cliff slide.One peson saved August: Helped Rye police arrest occupants of speed boats September: Towed boat to Hastings September: Rescued windsurfer October: Searched for overdue angling boat
